div.pre:
# SVG output set terminal svg size 340 110 set output "Integration_rectangle.svg" set samples 1000
# Configure border, axes, etc. unset key set xrange [-2:2] set yrange [-1.5:4.75] set border 3 lt 1 lc rgb "black" set grid set xtics autofreq 1 set ytics autofreq 2
# Define our function f(x) = x**2 + sin(2*pi*x)
# Draw rectangles set for [i = 0:15] object i+1 rect from -2+.25*i,0 to -2+.25*(i+1),f(-2+.25*(2*i+1)/2) fs empty border lt 3
# Plot plot f(x)
